{"tid":853003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(影片)俄男鼻塞難呼吸！淡定拿20公分刀插頭：想用頭吸氣","createTime":"2018-10-08T09:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T10:11:11.000Z","uid":205996,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cdc998687c16ecafc7eba4a7304d3dd91cedd3","tid":853003,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-08/656/20181008001753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-08%2F656%2F20181008001753.jpg&h=7229cac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯一名41歲男子，日前因鼻塞導致他難以呼吸，沒想到他竟突發奇想，決定用頭部呼吸，將8英寸（約20公分）長的刀子插進腦袋，隨後民眾經過田野時，發現頭上插著一把刀的男子，嚇得趕緊報警，所幸他沒有傷害到腦部，連醫師都驚呼是奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n根據《鏡報》報導，警方接獲報案後，立即趕至頓河畔羅斯托夫（Ростова-на-Дону），當時看見尤里（Yury Zhokhov）坐在田野中，而頭部插著一把刀，頂部裂了好大一個縫，但意識仍相當清楚，還能正常的說話，警方被嚇得狂叮嚀「你好好坐在那，不要亂動也不要彎腰」。<br />\n<br />\n尤里淡定的向警方表示，因為他鼻塞好幾天「我的鼻子無法呼吸，所以就想刺穿頭部，用頭呼吸」，便拿出20公分的廚房刀具，往頭部插進去想開洞，沒想到插到一半就卡住了，讓他的頭也無法呼吸。尤里送醫後，查看X光照片發現，刀柄恰好插進兩大腦的中間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-08/656/20181008001755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-08%2F656%2F20181008001755.jpg&h=b446c34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫師驚訝的表示，尤里能活下來是奇蹟，而刀柄插進去的位置很深，由於不敢貿然將刀取出，便請神經外科專家幫忙，刀才成功從尤里頭部取出。院方透露「這景象真的很恐怖，就連經驗豐富的護理師，看見時也感到相當害怕」。據了解，尤里出生於頓涅茨克(Donetsk)，原本在頓河畔羅斯托夫一間工廠擔任技術員，曾有進出精神病院的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dFjQwVcKMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdFjQwVcKMkw&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5IijCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5de8cffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dFjQwVcKMkw</a>"},{"pid":"765ed4d96ae7f391838cfbe3512108b41f3cdc4a","tid":853003,"uid":99607,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族"},{"pid":"52ddac94c73736c753ffd32e954d5c507848bedc","tid":853003,"uid":34469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195ef97d164b57c9c42188cc5f0f08aac75de425","tid":853003,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35b957019a220344df72fac0b04dfa9410e20fc","tid":853003,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"佢當自己係海豚鯨魚？"},{"pid":"839a42478aa7dc3fce36efce51ac6ef0483349d8","tid":853003,"uid":52023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"765ed4d96ae7f391838cfbe3512108b41f3cdc4a","tid":853003,"uid":99607,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"自己插頭都唔夠<br />\n仲要識行識走<br />\n點夠你玩呀"},{"pid":"eb17d91434b0eb5b8bf501aba12c523d31c85df6","tid":853003,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族係戰自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa85a0877883757170ea6b8d0f750f5bc9fd7f8","tid":853003,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族連痴線嘅都咁高攻高防+高幸運值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9801228e08b08170598bdefb7215c285e12f23ac","tid":853003,"uid":31200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"最緊要揸緊個信念"},{"pid":"e87c4e259e0ac5f51fb93618de3c17f954e553ab","tid":853003,"uid":45120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"鼻塞就插穿個頭透氣<br />\n我跟唔到個思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a716da30aef66db1354647ca83c15ff68dc436","tid":853003,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"